\v 3 <a name="02300700300004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Disse</a> o <a name="02300700300006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> a <a name="02300700300010" ll="SDBH:יְשַׁעְיָהוּ:000000">Isaías</a>: Agora, <a name="02300700300012" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">sai</a> tu com <a name="02300700300028" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">teu</a> <a name="02300700300028" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filho</a>, que se chama <a name="02300700300026" ll="SDBH:שְׁאָר יָשׁוּב:000000">Um</a>-<a name="02300700300026" ll="SDBH:שְׁאָר יָשׁוּב:000000">Resto</a>-<a name="02300700300026" ll="SDBH:שְׁאָר יָשׁוּב:000000">Volverá</a>, ao <a name="02300700300018" ll="SDBH:קרא:001000">encontro</a> de <a name="02300700300020" ll="SDBH:אָחָז:000000">Acaz</a>, que está na outra <a name="02300700300032" ll="SDBH:קָצֶה:000002">extremidade</a> do <a name="02300700300034" ll="SDBH:תְּעָלָה:000000">aqueduto</a> do <a name="02300700300038" ll="SDBH:בְּרֵכָה:000000">açude</a> <a name="02300700300042" ll="SDBH:עֶלְיֹון:000000">superior</a>, junto ao <a name="02300700300046" ll="SDBH:מְסִלָּה:000000">caminho</a> do <a name="02300700300048" ll="SDBH:שָׂדֶה:000001">campo</a> do <a name="02300700300050" ll="SDBH:כבס:000002">lavadeiro</a>, 
