\v 21 Pois eis que o <a name="02302602100006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="02302602100008" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">sai</a> do <a name="02302602100012" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">seu</a> <a name="02302602100012" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">lugar</a>, para <a name="02302602100016" ll="SDBH:פקד:000006">castigar</a> a <a name="02302602100018" ll="SDBH:עָוֹן:000000">iniquidade</a> dos <a name="02302602100020">moradores</a> da <a name="02302602100024" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>; a <a name="02302602100034" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> <a name="02302602100030" ll="SDBH:גלה:000009">descobrirá</a> o <a name="02302602100038" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000000" il="Blood">sangue</a> que embebeu e já não <a name="02302602100044" ll="SDBH:כסה:000000;SDBH:כסה:000001">encobrirá</a> aqueles que <a name="02302602100050" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">foram</a> <a name="02302602100050" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">mortos</a>.
\c 27
