\v 9 Portanto, com <a name="02302700900006" ll="SDBH:זֶה:000000;SDBH:זֹה:000000">isto</a> <a name="02302700900008" ll="SDBH:כפר:000005">será</a> <a name="02302700900008" ll="SDBH:כפר:000005">expiada</a> a <a name="02302700900010" ll="SDBH:עָוֹן:000000">culpa</a> <a name="02302700900012" ll="SDBH:יַעֲקֹב:000000">de</a> <a name="02302700900012" ll="SDBH:יַעֲקֹב:000000">Jacó</a>, e este é todo o <a name="02302700900020" ll="SDBH:פְּרִי:000003">fruto</a> do <a name="02302700900022" ll="SDBH:סור:000008">perdão</a> <a name="02302700900024" ll="SDBH:חַטָּאת:000000">do</a> <a name="02302700900024" ll="SDBH:חַטָּאת:000000">seu</a> <a name="02302700900024" ll="SDBH:חַטָּאת:000000">pecado</a>: quando o Senhor <a name="02302700900028" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000005">fizer</a> a todas as <a name="02302700900032" ll="SDBH:אֶבֶן:000001" il="tb041105516">pedras</a> do <a name="02302700900034" ll="SDBH:מִזְבֵּחַ:000000" il="HK00256;NBGlo20140504a;NBGlo20140504b;NBGlo20140504c;Realia:4.2.1b;Realia:4.2.3">altar</a> como pedras <a name="02302700900040" ll="SDBH:גִּר:000000">de</a> <a name="02302700900040" ll="SDBH:גִּר:000000">cal</a> <a name="02302700900042" ll="SDBH:נפץ:000000">feitas</a> <a name="02302700900042" ll="SDBH:נפץ:000000">em</a> <a name="02302700900042" ll="SDBH:נפץ:000000">pedaços</a>, não <a name="02302700900046">ficarão</a> <a name="02302700900046">em</a> <a name="02302700900046">pé</a> os <a name="02302700900048" ll="SDBH:אֲשֵׁרָה:000001">postes</a>-<a name="02302700900048" ll="SDBH:אֲשֵׁרָה:000001">ídolos</a> e os <a name="02302700900052" ll="SDBH:חַמָּן:000000" il="Incense_altar;NBGbs200904301_83;NBGlo20140504;Realia:4.6b;adr1305227007">altares</a> <a name="02302700900052" ll="SDBH:חַמָּן:000000" il="Incense_altar;NBGbs200904301_83;NBGlo20140504;Realia:4.6b;adr1305227007">do</a> <a name="02302700900052" ll="SDBH:חַמָּן:000000" il="Incense_altar;NBGbs200904301_83;NBGlo20140504;Realia:4.6b;adr1305227007">incenso</a>. 
