\v 13 <a name="02303301300002">Ouvi</a> <a name="02303301300004" ll="SDBH:רָחֹוק:000000">vós</a>, os <a name="02303301300004" ll="SDBH:רָחֹוק:000000">que</a> <a name="02303301300004" ll="SDBH:רָחֹוק:000000">estais</a> <a name="02303301300004" ll="SDBH:רָחֹוק:000000">longe</a>, o que <a name="02303301300008">tenho</a> <a name="02303301300008">feito</a>; e <a name="02303301300014">vós</a>, os <a name="02303301300014">que</a> <a name="02303301300014">estais</a> <a name="02303301300014">perto</a>, <a name="02303301300012">reconhecei</a> o <a name="02303301300016" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּרָה:000002">meu</a> <a name="02303301300016" ll="SDBH:גְּבוּרָה:000002">poder</a>.
    
\v 14 Os <a name="02303301400008" ll="SDBH:חַטָּא:000001">pecadores</a> em <a name="02303301400006" ll="SDBH:צִיֹּון:000000" il="tb060716478">Sião</a> <a name="02303301400002" ll="SDBH:פחד:000000">se</a> <a name="02303301400002" ll="SDBH:פחד:000000">assombram</a>, o <a name="02303301400012" ll="SDBH:רְעָדָה:000000">tremor</a> <a name="02303301400010" ll="SDBH:אחז:000002">se</a> <a name="02303301400010" ll="SDBH:אחז:000002">apodera</a> dos <a name="02303301400014" ll="SDBH:חָנֵף:000000">ímpios</a>; e eles perguntam: Quem dentre nós <a name="02303301400018" ll="SDBH:גור:000000">habitará</a> com o <a name="02303301400022" ll="SDBH:אֵשׁ:000000" il="Fire02">fogo</a> <a name="02303301400024" ll="SDBH:אכל:000002">devorador</a>? Quem dentre nós <a name="02303301400028" ll="SDBH:גור:000000">habitará</a> com <a name="02303301400032" ll="SDBH:מֹוקֵד:000000">chamas</a> <a name="02303301400034" ll="SDBH:עֹולָם:000000">eternas</a>? 
