\v 17 Os <a name="02303301700010" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">teus</a> <a name="02303301700010" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> <a name="02303301700008" ll="SDBH:חזה:000000">verão</a> o <a name="02303301700002" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> na <a name="02303301700006" ll="SDBH:יֳפִי:000000">sua</a> <a name="02303301700006" ll="SDBH:יֳפִי:000000">formosura</a>, <a name="02303301700012" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">verão</a> a <a name="02303301700014" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> que se estende <a name="02303301700016" ll="SDBH:מֶרְחָק:000000">até</a> <a name="02303301700016" ll="SDBH:מֶרְחָק:000000">longe</a>. 
\v 18 O <a name="02303301800002" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">teu</a> <a name="02303301800002" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">coração</a> <a name="02303301800004" ll="SDBH:הגה:000003">se</a> <a name="02303301800004" ll="SDBH:הגה:000003">recordará</a> dos <a name="02303301800006" ll="SDBH:אֵימָה:000000">terrores</a>, dizendo: Onde está aquele <a name="02303301800010" ll="SDBH:ספר:000000">que</a> <a name="02303301800010" ll="SDBH:ספר:000000">registrou</a>, onde, o <a name="02303301800014" ll="SDBH:שׁקל:000000">que</a> <a name="02303301800014" ll="SDBH:שׁקל:000000">pesou</a> o tributo, onde, o <a name="02303301800018" ll="SDBH:ספר:000000">que</a> <a name="02303301800018" ll="SDBH:ספר:000000">contou</a> as <a name="02303301800024" ll="SDBH:מִגְדָּל:000000" il="NBGpb20140401a">torres</a>? 
\v 19 Já não <a name="02303301900010" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">verás</a> aquele <a name="02303301900004" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> <a name="02303301900006" ll="SDBH:יעז:000000">atrevido</a>, <a name="02303301900012">povo</a> de <a name="02303301900016" ll="SDBH:שָׂפָה:000002">fala</a> <a name="02303301900014" ll="SDBH:עָמֵק:000000">obscura</a>, que não se pode <a name="02303301900020">entender</a>, e de <a name="02303301900024" ll="SDBH:לָשֹׁון:000002">língua</a> <a name="02303301900022" ll="SDBH:לעג:000001">bárbara</a>, <a name="02303301900026;02303301900028" ll="SDBH:בִּינָה:000000">ininteligível</a>. 
\v 20 <a name="02303302000002" ll="SDBH:חזה:000001">Olha</a> para <a name="02303302000004" ll="SDBH:צִיֹּון:000000" il="tb060716478">Sião</a>, a <a name="02303302000006" ll="SDBH:קִרְיָה:000000">cidade</a> das <a name="02303302000008" ll="SDBH:מֹועֵד:000002">nossas</a> <a name="02303302000008" ll="SDBH:מֹועֵד:000002">solenidades</a>; os <a name="02303302000010" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">teus</a> <a name="02303302000010" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> <a name="02303302000012" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">verão</a> a <a name="02303302000014" ll="SDBH:יְרוּשָׁלַ͏ִם:000000" il="NBGbs20090227-1_14;NBGbs20090227-1_34;NBGbs20090425-1_54;NBGbs20110228-1_79;Satellite Bible Atlas00024;jlm_hezekiah_city_d03;jlm_topography_d04">Jerusalém</a>, <a name="02303302000016" ll="SDBH:נָוֶה:000001">habitação</a> <a name="02303302000018" ll="SDBH:שַׁאֲנָן:000000">tranquila</a>, <a name="02303302000020" ll="SDBH:אֹהֶל:000003">tenda</a> que não <a name="02303302000024" ll="SDBH:צען:000000">será</a> <a name="02303302000024" ll="SDBH:צען:000000">removida</a>, <a name="02303302000030" ll="SDBH:יָתֵד:000000" il="Realia:3.2.2a">cujas</a> <a name="02303302000030" ll="SDBH:יָתֵד:000000" il="Realia:3.2.2a">estacas</a> <a name="02303302000034" ll="SDBH:נֵצַח:000000">nunca</a> <a name="02303302000028" ll="SDBH:נסע:000000">serão</a> <a name="02303302000028" ll="SDBH:נסע:000000">arrancadas</a>, nem <a name="02303302000044" ll="SDBH:נתק:000003">rebentada</a> nenhuma de <a name="02303302000040" ll="SDBH:חֶבֶל:000000" il="Realia:1.14">suas</a> <a name="02303302000040" ll="SDBH:חֶבֶל:000000" il="Realia:1.14">cordas</a>. 
\v 21 Mas o <a name="02303302100010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> ali nos será <a name="02303302100008" ll="SDBH:אַדִּיר:000000">grandioso</a>, fará as <a name="02303302100014" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">vezes</a> <a name="02303302100016" ll="SDBH:נָהָר:000015">de</a> <a name="02303302100016" ll="SDBH:נָהָר:000015">rios</a> e <a name="02303302100018" ll="SDBH:יְאֹר:000003">correntes</a> <a name="02303302100020;02303302100022" ll="SDBH:רָחָב:000000">largas</a>; <a name="02303302100030" ll="SDBH:אֳנִי:000001">barco</a> <a name="02303302100024" ll="SDBH:בַּל:000000">nenhum</a> <a name="02303302100032" ll="SDBH:שַׁיִט:000000">de</a> <a name="02303302100032" ll="SDBH:שַׁיִט:000000">remo</a> <a name="02303302100026" ll="SDBH:הלך:000000">passará</a> por eles, <a name="02303302100036" ll="SDBH:צִי:000000" il="HK00208;LB00213;Realia:8.1b;Realia:8.1c;Sail">navio</a> <a name="02303302100038" ll="SDBH:אַדִּיר:000000">grande</a> por eles não <a name="02303302100042" ll="SDBH:עבר:000000">navegará</a>. 
\v 22 Porque o <a name="02303302200004" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> é o <a name="02303302200006" ll="SDBH:שׁפט:000006" il="Tel-dan-israelite-gate-im-tor">nosso</a> <a name="02303302200006" ll="SDBH:שׁפט:000006" il="Tel-dan-israelite-gate-im-tor">juiz</a>, o <a name="02303302200008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> é o <a name="02303302200010" ll="SDBH:חקק:000003">nosso</a> <a name="02303302200010" ll="SDBH:חקק:000003">legislador</a>, o <a name="02303302200012" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> é o <a name="02303302200014" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">nosso</a> <a name="02303302200014" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">Rei</a>; ele <a name="02303302200018" ll="SDBH:ישׁע:000001">nos</a> <a name="02303302200018" ll="SDBH:ישׁע:000001">salvará</a>. 
\v 23 Agora, as <a name="02303302300004" ll="SDBH:חֶבֶל:000000" il="Realia:1.14">tuas</a> <a name="02303302300004" ll="SDBH:חֶבֶל:000000" il="Realia:1.14">enxárcias</a> <a name="02303302300002" ll="SDBH:נטשׁ:000000">estão</a> <a name="02303302300002" ll="SDBH:נטשׁ:000000">frouxas</a>; não podem <a name="02303302300008" ll="SDBH:חזק:000004">ter</a> <a name="02303302300010" ll="SDBH:כֵּן:002000">firme</a> o <a name="02303302300012" ll="SDBH:תֹּרֶן:000001">mastro</a>, nem <a name="02303302300016" ll="SDBH:פרשׂ:000000">estender</a> a <a name="02303302300018" ll="SDBH:נֵס:000002">vela</a>. Então, <a name="02303302300022" ll="SDBH:חלק:000006" tl="HOTTP3099">se</a> <a name="02303302300022" ll="SDBH:חלק:000006" tl="HOTTP3099">repartirá</a> a <a name="02303302300024" ll="SDBH:עַד:002000" tl="HOTTP3099">presa</a> <a name="02303302300026" ll="SDBH:שָׁלָל:000000" tl="HOTTP3099">de</a> <a name="02303302300028" ll="SDBH:מַרְבֶּה:000000">abundantes</a> <a name="02303302300026" ll="SDBH:שָׁלָל:000000" tl="HOTTP3099">despojos</a>; até os <a name="02303302300030" ll="SDBH:פִּסֵּחַ:000000">coxos</a> <a name="02303302300032" ll="SDBH:בזז:000000" il="Lachish_Relief-Booty">participarão</a> <a name="02303302300034" ll="SDBH:בַּז:000000" il="Lachish_Relief-Booty">dela</a>. 
\v 24 Nenhum <a name="02303302400008" ll="SDBH:שָׁכֵן:000000">morador</a> de Jerusalém <a name="02303302400006" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dirá</a>: <a name="02303302400010" ll="SDBH:חלה:000000">Estou</a> <a name="02303302400010" ll="SDBH:חלה:000000">doente</a>; porque ao <a name="02303302400014" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> que <a name="02303302400018">habita</a> nela, <a name="02303302400022" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000009">perdoar</a>-<a name="02303302400022" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000009">se</a>-lhe-<a name="02303302400022" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000009">á</a> a sua <a name="02303302400024" ll="SDBH:עָוֹן:000000">iniquidade</a>.
\c 34
\v 1 <a name="02303400100002" ll="SDBH:קרב:000000">Chegai</a>-<a name="02303400100002" ll="SDBH:קרב:000000">vos</a>, <a name="02303400100004" ll="SDBH:גֹּוי:000000">nações</a>, para <a name="02303400100008">ouvir</a>, e vós, <a name="02303400100012" ll="SDBH:לְאֹם:000000">povos</a>, <a name="02303400100014" ll="SDBH:קשׁב:000000">escutai</a>; <a name="02303400100016">ouça</a> a <a name="02303400100020" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> e a <a name="02303400100024" ll="SDBH:מְלֹא:000000">sua</a> <a name="02303400100024" ll="SDBH:מְלֹא:000000">plenitude</a>, o <a name="02303400100026" ll="SDBH:תֵּבֵל:000000">mundo</a> e tudo quanto <a name="02303400100032" ll="SDBH:צֶאֱצָא:000000">produz</a>. 
\v 2 Porque a <a name="02303400200004" ll="SDBH:קֶצֶף:000001">indignação</a> do <a name="02303400200008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> está contra todas as <a name="02303400200016" ll="SDBH:גֹּוי:000000">nações</a>, e o seu <a name="02303400200020" ll="SDBH:חֵמָה:001001">furor</a>, contra todo o <a name="02303400200026" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000003">exército</a> <a name="02303400200026" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000003">delas</a>; <a name="02303400200028" ll="SDBH:חרם:000003">ele</a> <a name="02303400200028" ll="SDBH:חרם:000003">as</a> <a name="02303400200028" ll="SDBH:חרם:000003">destinou</a> <a name="02303400200028" ll="SDBH:חרם:000003">para</a> a <a name="02303400200028" ll="SDBH:חרם:000003">destruição</a> e as <a name="02303400200030">entregou</a> à <a name="02303400200036" ll="SDBH:טֶבַח:000001">matança</a>. 
\v 3 Os <a name="02303400300004" ll="SDBH:חָלָל:000000">seus</a> <a name="02303400300004" ll="SDBH:חָלָל:000000">mortos</a> <a name="02303400300006" ll="SDBH:שׁלך:000000">serão</a> <a name="02303400300006" ll="SDBH:שׁלך:000000">lançados</a> <a name="02303400300006" ll="SDBH:שׁלך:000000">fora</a>, dos <a name="02303400300010" ll="SDBH:פֶּגֶר:000000">seus</a> <a name="02303400300010" ll="SDBH:פֶּגֶר:000000">cadáveres</a> <a name="02303400300012" ll="SDBH:עלה:000022">subirá</a> <a name="02303400300014" ll="SDBH:בְּאֹשׁ:000000">o</a> <a name="02303400300014" ll="SDBH:בְּאֹשׁ:000000">mau</a> <a name="02303400300014" ll="SDBH:בְּאֹשׁ:000000">cheiro</a>, e do <a name="02303400300024" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000000" il="Blood">sangue</a> <a name="02303400300024" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000000" il="Blood">deles</a> os <a name="02303400300020" ll="SDBH:הַר:000000">montes</a> <a name="02303400300018" ll="SDBH:מסס:000003">se</a> <a name="02303400300018" ll="SDBH:מסס:000003">inundarão</a>. 
\v 4 Todo o <a name="02303400400008" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000004">exército</a> dos <a name="02303400400012" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">céus</a> <a name="02303400400004" ll="SDBH:מקק:000002">se</a> <a name="02303400400004" ll="SDBH:מקק:000002">dissolverá</a>, e os <a name="02303400400026" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">céus</a> <a name="02303400400016" ll="SDBH:גלל:000001">se</a> <a name="02303400400016" ll="SDBH:גלל:000001">enrolarão</a> como <a name="02303400400022">um</a> <a name="02303400400022">pergaminho</a>; todo o <a name="02303400400032" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000004">seu</a> <a name="02303400400032" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000004">exército</a> <a name="02303400400034" ll="SDBH:נבל:000000">cairá</a>, como <a name="02303400400038" ll="SDBH:נבל:000000">cai</a> a <a name="02303400400040" ll="SDBH:עָלֶה:000000">folha</a> da <a name="02303400400044" ll="SDBH:גֶּפֶן:000001" il="Flora:2.12a;Flora:2.12b;HK00112;LB00107;tb061504248;tb111706130;vineyard1679, rp">vide</a> e a folha da <a name="02303400400054" ll="SDBH:תְּאֵנָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d;figtree1689, rp">figueira</a>.
    
\v 5 Porque a <a name="02303400500012" ll="SDBH:חֶרֶב:000001" il="NBGmk20130711a;NBGmk20130711b;NBGmk20130711c;StraightSword-02-003;adr1305240787;tb061616732" tl="HOTTP3101">minha</a> <a name="02303400500012" ll="SDBH:חֶרֶב:000001" il="NBGmk20130711a;NBGmk20130711b;NBGmk20130711c;StraightSword-02-003;adr1305240787;tb061616732" tl="HOTTP3101">espada</a> <a name="02303400500004" ll="SDBH:רוה:000001" tl="HOTTP3100">se</a> <a name="02303400500004" ll="SDBH:רוה:000001" tl="HOTTP3100">embriagou</a> nos <a name="02303400500010" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000000">céus</a>; eis que, para <a name="02303400500032" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000002">exercer</a> <a name="02303400500032" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000002">juízo</a>, <a name="02303400500020" ll="SDBH:ירד:000000">desce</a> sobre <a name="02303400500018" ll="SDBH:אֱדֹום:000001" il="NBGbs20120713-539;tb061504246">Edom</a> e sobre o <a name="02303400500026" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> que destinei para a <a name="02303400500028" ll="SDBH:חֵרֶם:001000" tl="HOTTP3101">destruição</a>. 
\v 6 A <a name="02303400600002" ll="SDBH:חֶרֶב:000001" il="NBGmk20130711a;NBGmk20130711b;NBGmk20130711c;StraightSword-02-003;adr1305240787;tb061616732">espada</a> do <a name="02303400600006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> está <a name="02303400600008" ll="SDBH:מלא:000000">cheia</a> de <a name="02303400600010" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000000" il="Blood">sangue</a>, <a name="02303400600012" ll="SDBH:דשׁן:000002">engrossada</a> da <a name="02303400600016" ll="SDBH:חֵלֶב:000000">gordura</a> e do <a name="02303400600020" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000000" il="Blood">sangue</a> de <a name="02303400600022" ll="SDBH:כַּר:000001">cordeiros</a> e de <a name="02303400600026" ll="SDBH:עַתּוּד:000000" il="BK00016;NBGbs20120208-08;tb030407773">bodes</a>, da <a name="02303400600030" ll="SDBH:חֵלֶב:000000">gordura</a> dos <a name="02303400600032" ll="SDBH:כִּלְיָה:000000">rins</a> de <a name="02303400600034" ll="SDBH:אַיִל:000000" il="Ram">carneiros</a>; porque o <a name="02303400600042" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> tem <a name="02303400600038" ll="SDBH:זֶבַח:000000">sacrifício</a> em <a name="02303400600046" ll="SDBH:בָּצְרָה:001000" il="tb061404287">Bozra</a> e <a name="02303400600052" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000003">grande</a> <a name="02303400600050" ll="SDBH:טֶבַח:000000">matança</a> na <a name="02303400600056" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> de <a name="02303400600058" ll="SDBH:אֱדֹום:000001" il="NBGbs20120713-539;tb061504246">Edom</a>. 
\v 7 Os <a name="02303400700006" ll="SDBH:רְאֵם:000000" il="Fauna:2.34a;Fauna:2.34b;Fauna:2.34c;Fauna:2.34d;Fauna:2.34e">bois</a> <a name="02303400700006" ll="SDBH:רְאֵם:000000" il="Fauna:2.34a;Fauna:2.34b;Fauna:2.34c;Fauna:2.34d;Fauna:2.34e">selvagens</a> <a name="02303400700004" ll="SDBH:ירד:000004">cairão</a> com eles, e os <a name="02303400700012" ll="SDBH:פַּר:000000" il="Fauna:2.10;LB00022;rs032002108">novilhos</a>, com os <a name="02303400700016" ll="SDBH:אַבִּיר:000002">touros</a>; a <a name="02303400700022" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">sua</a> <a name="02303400700022" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> <a name="02303400700020" ll="SDBH:רוה:000001">se</a> <a name="02303400700020" ll="SDBH:רוה:000001">embriagará</a> de <a name="02303400700026" ll="SDBH:דָּם:000000" il="Blood">sangue</a>, e o <a name="02303400700030" ll="SDBH:עָפָר:000000">seu</a> <a name="02303400700030" ll="SDBH:עָפָר:000000">pó</a> <a name="02303400700036" ll="SDBH:דשׁן:000004">se</a> <a name="02303400700036" ll="SDBH:דשׁן:000004">tornará</a> <a name="02303400700036" ll="SDBH:דשׁן:000004">fértil</a> com a <a name="02303400700034" ll="SDBH:חֵלֶב:000000">gordura</a>.
    
\v 8 Porque será o <a name="02303400800004" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000006">dia</a> <a name="02303400800006" ll="SDBH:נָקָם:000000">da</a> <a name="02303400800006" ll="SDBH:נָקָם:000000">vingança</a> do <a name="02303400800010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="02303400800012" ll="SDBH:שָׁנָה:000000">ano</a> de <a name="02303400800014" ll="SDBH:שִׁלּוּם:000001">retribuições</a> pela <a name="02303400800018" ll="SDBH:רִיב:000000">causa</a> de <a name="02303400800020" ll="SDBH:צִיֹּון:000000" il="tb060716478">Sião</a>. 
\v 9 Os <a name="02303400900006" ll="SDBH:נַחַל:000000" il="NBGbs20090428-1_39;tb110603119">ribeiros</a> de Edom <a name="02303400900004" ll="SDBH:הפך:000008">se</a> <a name="02303400900004" ll="SDBH:הפך:000008">transformarão</a> em <a name="02303400900010" ll="SDBH:זֶפֶת:000000" il="Tar;Tar-fishing-boat">piche</a>, e o <a name="02303400900014" ll="SDBH:עָפָר:000000">seu</a> <a name="02303400900014" ll="SDBH:עָפָר:000000">pó</a>, em <a name="02303400900018" ll="SDBH:גָּפְרִית:000000" il="Sulphur1;Sulphur2">enxofre</a>; a <a name="02303400900024" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">sua</a> <a name="02303400900024" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> se tornará em <a name="02303400900028" ll="SDBH:זֶפֶת:000000" il="Tar;Tar-fishing-boat">piche</a> <a name="02303400900030" ll="SDBH:בער:000000">ardente</a>. 
\v 10 Nem de <a name="02303401000002" ll="SDBH:לַיְלָה:000000">noite</a> nem <a name="02303401000006" ll="SDBH:יֹומָם:000000">de</a> <a name="02303401000006" ll="SDBH:יֹומָם:000000">dia</a> <a name="02303401000010" ll="SDBH:כבה:000000">se</a> <a name="02303401000010" ll="SDBH:כבה:000000">apagará</a>; <a name="02303401000016" ll="SDBH:עלה:000000">subirá</a> para <a name="02303401000014" ll="SDBH:עֹולָם:000000">sempre</a> a <a name="02303401000018" ll="SDBH:עָשָׁן:000000" il="Smoke">sua</a> <a name="02303401000018" ll="SDBH:עָשָׁן:000000" il="Smoke">fumaça</a>; de <a name="02303401000022" ll="SDBH:דֹּור:001000">geração</a> em <a name="02303401000026" ll="SDBH:דֹּור:001000">geração</a> <a name="02303401000028" ll="SDBH:חרב:000002">será</a> <a name="02303401000028" ll="SDBH:חרב:000002">assolada</a>, e para <a name="02303401000032;02303401000034" ll="SDBH:נֵצַח:000001">todo</a> <a name="02303401000032;02303401000034" ll="SDBH:נֵצַח:000001">o</a> <a name="02303401000032;02303401000034" ll="SDBH:נֵצַח:000001">sempre</a> ninguém <a name="02303401000038" ll="SDBH:עבר:000000">passará</a> por ela. 
\v 11 Mas o <a name="02303401100006" ll="SDBH:קָאָת:000000">pelicano</a> e o <a name="02303401100010" ll="SDBH:קִפֹּד:000000">ouriço</a> <a name="02303401100004" ll="SDBH:ירשׁ:000002">a</a> <a name="02303401100004" ll="SDBH:ירשׁ:000002">possuirão</a>; o <a name="02303401100014" ll="SDBH:יַנְשֹׁוף:000000" il="Fauna:3.17.2">bufo</a> e o <a name="02303401100018" ll="SDBH:עֹורֵב:000000" il="Brown-necked_raven;Corvus_cornix">corvo</a> <a name="02303401100020" ll="SDBH:שׁכן:000000">habitarão</a> nela. <a name="02303401100026" ll="SDBH:נטה:001000">Estender</a>-<a name="02303401100026" ll="SDBH:נטה:001000">se</a>-<a name="02303401100026" ll="SDBH:נטה:001000">á</a> sobre ela o <a name="02303401100030" ll="SDBH:קַו:000000">cordel</a> <a name="02303401100032" ll="SDBH:תֹּהוּ:000000">de</a> <a name="02303401100032" ll="SDBH:תֹּהוּ:000000">destruição</a> e o <a name="02303401100036" ll="SDBH:אֶבֶן:000005">prumo</a> <a name="02303401100038" ll="SDBH:בֹּהוּ:000000">de</a> <a name="02303401100038" ll="SDBH:בֹּהוּ:000000">ruína</a>. 
\v 12 Já não haverá <a name="02303401200002" ll="SDBH:חֹר:001000" tl="HOTTP3103">nobres</a> para <a name="02303401200012" ll="SDBH:קרא:000007">proclamarem</a> um <a name="02303401200010" ll="SDBH:מְלוּכָה:000000">rei</a>; os <a name="02303401200018" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">seus</a> <a name="02303401200018" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">príncipes</a> já não <a name="02303401200022" ll="SDBH:אֶפֶס:000003">existem</a>. 
\v 13 Nos <a name="02303401300006" ll="SDBH:אַרְמֹון:000000">seus</a> <a name="02303401300006" ll="SDBH:אַרְמֹון:000000">palácios</a>, <a name="02303401300004" ll="SDBH:עלה:000010">crescerão</a> <a name="02303401300008" ll="SDBH:סִירָה:000000" il="HK00122;LB00121">espinhos</a>, e <a name="02303401300010" ll="SDBH:קִמֹּושׂ:000000" il="Flora:6.2.2b">urtigas</a> e <a name="02303401300014" ll="SDBH:חֹוחַ:000000" il="Flora:6.2.1a;Flora:6.2.1b;Flora:6.2.1c;Flora:6.2.1d;Flora:6.2.1e;Sarcopoterium_Spinosum">cardos</a>, nas <a name="02303401300018" ll="SDBH:מִבְצָר:000000">suas</a> <a name="02303401300018" ll="SDBH:מִבְצָר:000000">fortalezas</a>; será uma <a name="02303401300024" ll="SDBH:נָוֶה:000001">habitação</a> de <a name="02303401300026" ll="SDBH:תַּן:000000" il="BK00051;Fauna:2.22a;Fauna:2.22b;Fauna:2.22c">chacais</a> e <a name="02303401300028" ll="SDBH:חָצִיר:001000">morada</a> de <a name="02303401300032;02303401300034" ll="SDBH:בַּת:002000;SDBH:יַעֲנָה:000000" il="Fauna:3.16">avestruzes</a>. 
\v 14 As <a name="02303401400006" ll="SDBH:צִי:000001" il="Striped_Hyena_5;tb110902455">feras</a> <a name="02303401400006" ll="SDBH:צִי:000001" il="Striped_Hyena_5;tb110902455">do</a> <a name="02303401400006" ll="SDBH:צִי:000001" il="Striped_Hyena_5;tb110902455">deserto</a> <a name="02303401400004" ll="SDBH:פגשׁ:000000">se</a> <a name="02303401400004" ll="SDBH:פגשׁ:000000">encontrarão</a> com as <a name="02303401400010" ll="SDBH:אִי:000001" il="BK00051;Fauna:2.22a;Fauna:2.22b;Fauna:2.22c;Striped_Hyena_5;tb110902455">hienas</a>, e os <a name="02303401400014" ll="SDBH:שָׂעִיר:000001">sátiros</a> <a name="02303401400020" ll="SDBH:קרא:000000">clamarão</a> uns para os <a name="02303401400018" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">outros</a>; <a name="02303401400028" ll="SDBH:לִילִית:000000">fantasmas</a> ali <a name="02303401400026" ll="SDBH:רגע:002000">pousarão</a> e <a name="02303401400032" ll="SDBH:מצא:000000">acharão</a> para si <a name="02303401400036" ll="SDBH:מָנֹוחַ:000001">lugar</a> <a name="02303401400036" ll="SDBH:מָנֹוחַ:000001">de</a> <a name="02303401400036" ll="SDBH:מָנֹוחַ:000001">repouso</a>. 
\v 15 <a name="02303401500004" ll="SDBH:קנן:000000">Aninhar</a>-<a name="02303401500004" ll="SDBH:קנן:000000">se</a>-<a name="02303401500004" ll="SDBH:קנן:000000">á</a> ali a <a name="02303401500006" ll="SDBH:קִפֹּוז:000000">coruja</a>, e <a name="02303401500010" ll="SDBH:מלט:000002">porá</a> os <a name="02303401500010" ll="SDBH:מלט:000002">seus</a> <a name="02303401500010" ll="SDBH:מלט:000002">ovos</a>, e os <a name="02303401500014" ll="SDBH:בקע:000007">chocará</a>, e na <a name="02303401500022" ll="SDBH:צֵל:000001">sombra</a> <a name="02303401500018" ll="SDBH:דגר:000000">abrigará</a> os seus filhotes; também ali os <a name="02303401500030" ll="SDBH:דַּיָּה:000000">abutres</a> <a name="02303401500028" ll="SDBH:קבץ:000000">se</a> <a name="02303401500028" ll="SDBH:קבץ:000000">ajuntarão</a>, <a name="02303401500032" ll="SDBH:אִשָּׁה:000003">um</a> com <a name="02303401500034" ll="SDBH:רְעוּת:000000">o</a> <a name="02303401500034" ll="SDBH:רְעוּת:000000">outro</a>.
    
