\v 4 <a name="02303600400008">Rabsaqué</a> lhes <a name="02303600400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: <a name="02303600400010" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Dizei</a> a <a name="02303600400016" ll="SDBH:חִזְקִיָּה:000000" il="NBGbs20110228-1_79;Satellite Bible Atlas00069;adr1305123466;jlm_hezekiah_city_d03;tb032014271;tb110705561">Ezequias</a>: Assim <a name="02303600400020" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="02303600400028" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000002">sumo</a> <a name="02303600400024" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>, o <a name="02303600400030" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> da <a name="02303600400032" ll="SDBH:אַשּׁוּר:000001" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00066;adr1306212575;adr1306212845;adr1311202840;adr1311203118">Assíria</a>: Que <a name="02303600400038" ll="SDBH:בִּטָּחֹון:000000">confiança</a> é essa em que <a name="02303600400046" ll="SDBH:בטח:000001">te</a> <a name="02303600400046" ll="SDBH:בטח:000001">estribas</a>? 
