\v 19 Não <a name="02304501900010" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">falei</a> em <a name="02304501900008" ll="SDBH:סֵתֶר:000001">segredo</a>, nem em <a name="02304501900014" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">lugar</a> algum <a name="02304501900018" ll="SDBH:חֹשֶׁךְ:000000">de</a> <a name="02304501900018" ll="SDBH:חֹשֶׁךְ:000000">trevas</a> da <a name="02304501900016" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>; não <a name="02304501900022" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> à <a name="02304501900026" ll="SDBH:זֶרַע:000004" il="Children_of_Kabul,_Afghanistan">descendência</a> de <a name="02304501900028" ll="SDBH:יַעֲקֹב:000000">Jacó</a>: <a name="02304501900032" ll="SDBH:בקשׁ:000003" il="LB00269;LB00270;LB00271;NBGbs20110228-1_61-2;NBGmk20140526">Buscai</a>-<a name="02304501900032" ll="SDBH:בקשׁ:000003" il="LB00269;LB00270;LB00271;NBGbs20110228-1_61-2;NBGmk20140526">me</a> em <a name="02304501900030" ll="SDBH:תֹּהוּ:000000">vão</a>; eu, o <a name="02304501900036" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="02304501900038" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">falo</a> a <a name="02304501900040" ll="SDBH:צֶדֶק:000001">verdade</a> e <a name="02304501900042" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">proclamo</a> o que é <a name="02304501900044" ll="SDBH:מֵישָׁרִים:000000">direito</a>. 
