5;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">Casa</a> <a name="02305600700042" ll="SDBH:תְּפִלָּה:000000">de</a> <a name="02305600700042" ll="SDBH:תְּפִלָּה:000000">Oração</a> para todos os <a name="02305600700052" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povos</a>. 
